Prior art acknowledgements
--------------------------

The OVAL parsing and Red Hat advisory-extraction logic in this library was
informed by reading two Apache-2.0-licensed codebases from the Aqua Security
project:

  * aquasecurity/trivy-db
    Specifically pkg/vulnsrc/redhat-oval — the Red Hat OVAL consumer inside
    trivy-db's build pipeline.
    https://github.com/aquasecurity/trivy-db

  * aquasecurity/vuln-list-update
    Specifically redhat/oval — the Red Hat OVAL fetcher + normaliser.
    https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-update

oval-to-vex is not derived from these projects. Their source was read as
prior art to understand the Red Hat OVAL feed's quirks. No code was copied.
This library's output shape (VEX-style Statements) differs from trivy-db's
BoltDB schema, and its fetch model differs from vuln-list-update's
filesystem-based pipeline.
